          0,
          "This game is essentially a miniseries set in the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Borderlands"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " universe and good god they nailed it. Set between "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Borderlands 2 "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "and "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Borderlands 3"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Tales From the Borderlands"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " follows Hyperion executive Rhys as he learns about life on Pandora. The characters are well cast, well written and more lifelike than anything seen in a "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Borderlands "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "game before. That is perhaps the best thing about this game: there is depth of writing and characterization that we just don’t get in most video game scripts, even the more story-driven ones like "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "The Last of Us"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". "
        ]
