      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The talent among the cast is amazing. Between big names like Patrick Warburton (Kronk in "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "The Emperor's New Groove"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "), an intelligent script and flawless delivery, this game is nothing short of cinema. Scripts in the mainline games often feel limited by the action-driven nature of the series but this entry is much more humane and deep, while maintaining the comedic timing and style of the series."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The music is minimal but for a game like this, less is more. The instrumental soundtrack, while subtle, is beautifully composed and pairs well with the tone established within the dialogue. In a nutshell, "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Tales From The Borderlands"
        ],
